A Place In The Sun presenter Danni Menzies wowed fans on social media as the blonde beauty touched down in Ibiza in her latest getaway abroad. The 33-year-old put her taut abs and toned legs on full display as she took to Instagram and shared a series of photos wearing a tiny two-piece bikini. The property expert also unveiled her inked tattoos in a candid mirror selfie as she accessoried her look with a wide-brimmed hat and a pair of sunglasses. She accompanied her beach attire with gold jewellery as she shared some more photos of her full outfit, which the presenter captioned: "I finally made it." The on-screen star added the hashtags: "#ibiza #ibizastyle #ibiza2022 #ibiza."